data.description: This 1449 square foot single family home has 4 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 223 W 300 S, Saint George, UT 84770.
data.whatILove:
Everything inside is updated and comfy with a nice layout, including a bay window in the front room. There are four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The kitchen was recently remodeled with all new cabinets and appliances, including a dishwasher. The home has central air and heating and a swamp cooler. All windows are dual pane, and most of them are tinted for energy savings. Much of the hot and cold water supply plumbing has been replaced. Other new items on the house include the roof, replaced in 8/2015, hot water heater replaced 12/2014, and garbage disposal 6/2015.

The back yard has a shed, playground and a gazebo for relaxing. All landscaping is complete and has two separate timers for watering front and back yards separately. Also, the yard is completely fenced, which is awesome for little children.

We have small children, so please call for an appointment to view. Call or text Shawn
